You downloaded KMonop from CVS
------------------------------

cd $(srcdir)/kdenonbeta && make -f Makefile.cvs && ./configure)
cd $(srcdir)/kdenonbeta/libkdegames && make && make install
cd $(srcdir)/kdenonbeta/kmonop && make && make install

You downloaded a release tarball
--------------------------------

./configure && make && make install

Running the game
----------------

Click on K->Games->Board->KMonop or run kmonop from the konsole or minicli.

Please note that KMonop is only a client! You will need to connect to a
monopd server on the Internet or run one locally! See the README file for
more details on the KMonop/monopd client/server concept.
